suncertify.presentation
Class SearchRecordsExactFilter

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.presentation.SearchRecordsExactFilter

public class SearchRecordsExactFilter
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to filter records for the GUI as it requires exact matches to the search criteria. It takes a HashMap which was returned from BookingBusinessAdapterImp class which in turn was returned from the Datathe class and filers the HashMap and populates a new HashMap with record numbers and contractors objects using same search criteria but only populates the new HashMap with exact matches rather than matching the beginning part of the field being matched.

Version:
1.0
Author:
